blogPost.excerpt:
Oral Roberts shocked the world and took down Ohio State in OT. Kevin Obanor and Max Abmas scored 30 and 29 points for the Golden Eagles, respectively. Oral Roberts became just the 9th 15 seed ever to upset a 2 seed in NCAA tournament history, and the first since Middle Tennessee knocked off Michigan State in 2016. Watch the full extended highlights here.

Watch highlights, game recaps, and much more from the 2021 NCAA Division I Men’s Basketball Tournament on the official NCAA March Madness YouTube channel. Subscribe now to be updated on the latest videos: http://www.youtube.com/marchmadness?sub_confirmation=1

localize.title: 奥拉罗伯茨 vs 俄亥俄州立大学 - 首轮NCAA锦标赛延长的精彩片段
localize.description:
奥拉罗伯茨震惊了世界，在加时赛中拿下了俄亥俄州立大学。凯文-奥班诺和马克斯-阿巴斯分别为金雕队拿下30分和29分。奥拉-罗伯茨成为NCAA锦标赛历史上第9个击败2号种子的15号种子，也是自2016年中田纳西州淘汰密歇根州立大学以来的第一个。在这里观看完整的扩展亮点。

在NCAA疯狂三月官方YouTube频道观看2021年NCAA一级男篮锦标赛的亮点、比赛回顾以及更多内容。立即订阅以获得最新视频的更新：http://www.youtube.com/marchmadness?sub_confirmation=1。

next.excerpt:
Minecraft, But Every Mob Looks Like A Pig... This was super hilarious! We never knew what was coming at us!

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @sapnap
➽ Twitch - @sapnap
➽ Instagram - @sapnapinsta

Dream- @Dream 
George- @GeorgeNotFound

This is a Minecraft 1.16 mod that makes all mobs look like pigs. This made the game a lot more crazy because we never knew what mob we were dealing with. This was really funny and made even the most simple tasks like getting food dangerous. I really love doing these types of fun challenges with my friends!

localize.title: Minecraft，但每个黑帮看起来像猪... ...
localize.description:
Minecraft，但每个黑帮看起来像猪... ... 这是超级搞笑的！我们永远不知道什么在我们身上!

关注我的社交。
➽ Twitter - @sapnap
➽ Twitch - @sapnap
➽ Instagram - @sapnapinsta

梦想- @梦想 
George- @GeorgeNotFound

这是一个Minecraft 1.16 mod，让所有的暴民看起来像猪。这使得游戏更加疯狂，因为我们永远不知道我们正在处理什么暴民。这真的很有趣，甚至最简单的任务，如获取食物的危险。我真的很喜欢和我的朋友们一起做这些类型的有趣挑战!
